# Title: Use of Scriptrunner.exe
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-07-01
# Level: medium
# Description: The "ScriptRunner.exe" binary can be abused to proxy execution through it and bypass possible whitelisting
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_scriptrunner.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate use when App-v is deployed

CommandLine="* -appvscript *" Image="*\\ScriptRunner.exe" OR OriginalFileName="ScriptRunner.exe"